snippet.title: Paralegal Reacts To AMBER HEARD TESTIMONY 2 in JOHNNY DEPP V. NGN *reupload*
snippet.description:
PARALEGAL REACTS TO JOHNNY DEPP V. AMBER HEARD

Background video from: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=k7lVOMfFstU check them out for video ofJohnny Depp and Amber Heard arriving and exiting the UK High Court.

So today I reacted to Amber Heard’s testimony day 2, I obtained a copy of the transcript via Nick Wallis' website, https://www.nickwallis.com 

Also gonna link Lost Beyond Pluto, who is a lawyer who breaks down the legality of this case very professionally: https://www.youtube.com/c/lostbeyondpluto

Link to Incredibly Average, he has covered this case in depth from beginning to very recently.. including animated re-enactments etc. Highly recommend!: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCg0C-N_MPYYOXyF4T3jMxNQ

Thank you so much for the love on my last two videos I really appreciate it! It's really motivating me to keep it up. I hope this was helpful or enjoyable in some way. I plan to keep up with this case so stay tuned and make sure you are subscribed and turn your notification bell on!
